asset.author: Hoover
asset.hookText: Hi Magic Clean. We saw your review on Hoover.com. Your T-Series may shut down if there's not enough air getting to the motor. This should be an easy fix. We put together a quick video for you to help you get it working properly again. Let us know if you need more help! - Sharon
